description: Number of unlabeled unit interval graphs with n nodes.
references: S. R. Finch, Mathematical Constants, Cambridge, 2003, Section 5.6.7.
Hanlon, Phil; Counting interval graphs. Trans. Amer. Math. Soc. 272 (1982), no. 2, 383-426.
N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).
R. W. Robinson, Numerical implementation of graph counting algorithms, AGRC Grant, Math. Dept., Univ. Newcastle, Australia, 1980.
links: R. W. Robinson, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..190
formula: G.f. A(x) = x + 2x^2 + 4x^3 + 9x^4 + 21x^5 + ... satisfies 1 + A(x) = exp( Sum_{k >= 1} psi(x^k)/k ), where psi(x) = (1+2*x-sqrt(1-4*x)*sqrt(1-4*x^2))/(4*sqrt(1-4*x^2)) is the g.f. for A007123.For asymptotics, see for example Finch.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
